@node main Call

                                 @{b}Call, v2.00
                                 -------------@{ub}

Call replaces the original Call script providing redialling. This
program is freeware and freely distributable. ©1996 by Sami Klemola.
All Rights Reserved.

         @{" Command specification                " link Call_1}
